diagrams.code:
// title
title HippoRAG data model

// define tables
queries [icon: message-square, color: lightblue] {
  id string pk
  user_input text
  timestamp datetime
  retrieval_model string fk
  generator_model string fk
}

memory_systems [icon: database, color: orange] {
  id string pk
  type string        // episodic | semantic | working
  description text
}

memory_entries [icon: file, color: yellow] {
  id string pk
  system_id string fk
  content text
  embedding vector
  timestamp datetime
  importance float
}

models [icon: cpu, color: pink] {
  id string pk
  name string
  version string
  type string        // retrieval | generation | encoder
}

encodings [icon: settings, color: gray] {
  id string pk
  entry_id string fk
  model_id string fk
  vector vector
  created_at datetime
}

retrievals [icon: search, color: purple] {
  id string pk
  query_id string fk
  entry_id string fk
  score float
  retrieved_at datetime
}

responses [icon: message-circle, color: green] {
  id string pk
  query_id string fk
  content text
  generated_at datetime
}

// define relationships
queries.retrieval_model > models.id
queries.generator_model  > models.id

memory_entries.system_id  > memory_systems.id

encodings.entry_id       > memory_entries.id
encodings.model_id       > models.id

retrievals.query_id      > queries.id
retrievals.entry_id      > memory_entries.id

responses.query_id       > queries.id
